title: SouthernCharm: Nashville Predators
description:
The "Southern Charm" guys head to Nashville to terrorize the local female population while the women back in Charleston gather for a celebration of artichokes at Patricia's house. In the end, Austen realizes he's been entranced by Shep, which could possibly lead to a reunion with him and Madison. WHO KNOWS??

See acast.com/privacy for privacy and opt-out information.
